@startuml
title Feature 031 - цены, акции, offers, gifts и бенефиты

actor "Pricing manager" as PricingManager
actor "Promotions manager" as PromotionsManager
actor "Бизнес-администратор" as BusinessAdmin
participant "Admin frontend\n/admin/pricing" as AdminUi
participant "admin-pricing API\n/module admin-pricing" as AdminPricing
database "admin_pricing_*" as PricingDb
participant "admin-pim API\npublished products" as AdminPim
participant "admin-catalog API\ncampaign windows" as AdminCatalog
participant "catalog/cart/checkout\npricing consumers" as Consumers
participant "Audit trail" as Audit

PricingManager -> AdminUi: открывает workspace цен и промо
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: GET /price-lists?campaignId=CAM-2026-05
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: search price lists
PricingDb --> AdminPricing: page
AdminPricing --> AdminUi: PriceListPage

PricingManager -> AdminUi: создает price list PL-RU-2026-05
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /price-lists
AdminPricing -> AdminCatalog: validate campaignId and active window
AdminCatalog --> AdminPricing: campaign valid
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert admin_pricing_price_list
AdminPricing -> Audit: PRICE_LIST_CREATED
AdminPricing --> AdminUi: PriceListResponse

PricingManager -> AdminUi: добавляет базовую цену SKU
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /price-lists/{id}/prices
AdminPricing -> AdminPim: validate SKU is published
AdminPim --> AdminPricing: product published
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: check active interval overlap
alt price period overlaps
  AdminPricing --> AdminUi: 409 STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PRICING_PRICE_PERIOD_OVERLAP
else valid price
  AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert admin_pricing_price
  AdminPricing -> Audit: PRICE_CREATED
  AdminPricing --> AdminUi: BasePriceResponse
end

PricingManager -> AdminUi: добавляет promo price и segment rule
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /promo-prices, POST /segment-rules
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: validate currency, margin, priority
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert promo_price and segment_rule
AdminPricing -> Audit: PROMO_PRICE_CREATED, SEGMENT_RULE_CREATED
AdminPricing --> AdminUi: responses with status DRAFT

PromotionsManager -> AdminUi: создает promotion, offer, bundle и gift
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /promotions
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert admin_pricing_promotion
AdminPricing -> Audit: PROMOTION_CREATED
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /promotions/{id}/offers
AdminPricing -> AdminPim: validate offer item SKU list
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert shopping_offer and offer_item
AdminPricing -> Audit: SHOPPING_OFFER_CREATED
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /promotions/{id}/gift-rules
AdminPricing -> AdminPim: validate gift SKU is published
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: insert gift_rule
AdminPricing -> Audit: GIFT_RULE_CREATED

BusinessAdmin -> AdminUi: запускает publish с Idempotency-Key
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /publish
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: load price list, prices, promotions, offers, gifts
AdminPricing -> AdminPim: validate published products and gift SKUs
AdminPricing -> AdminCatalog: validate campaign window
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: preflight overlap, margin, compatibility
alt preflight failed
  AdminPricing -> Audit: PRICING_PUBLISH_REJECTED
  AdminPricing --> AdminUi: 409 STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PRICING_PREFLIGHT_FAILED
else preflight valid
  AdminPricing -> PricingDb: activate price list and promotions atomically
  AdminPricing -> Audit: PRICING_PUBLISHED
  AdminPricing --> AdminUi: PublishPricingResponse(PUBLISHED)
  Consumers -> AdminPricing: read active price rules/offers by campaign and segment
  AdminPricing -> PricingDb: query active commercial conditions
  AdminPricing --> Consumers: base price, promo price, offers, gifts, mnemonic reasons
end

BusinessAdmin -> AdminUi: emergency pause offer
AdminUi -> AdminPricing: POST /offers/{offerId}/pause
AdminPricing -> PricingDb: set offer status PAUSED
AdminPricing -> Audit: SHOPPING_OFFER_PAUSED(reasonCode)
AdminPricing --> AdminUi: ShoppingOfferResponse(PAUSED)
Consumers -> AdminPricing: recalculation request
AdminPricing --> Consumers: paused offer excluded

@enduml
